Package graph

package graph
The Graph package contains classes related to graph representations and operations. It provides classes for creating weighted and weightless graphs, managing nodes and edges, and performing graph operations.
  • Class
    Description
    AbstractGraph
    The AbstractGraph class provides a base implementation for common graph operations.
    Edge
    The Edge class represents an edge in a graph.
    Graph
    The Graph class represents an unweighted graph.
    HamiltonianCycle
    The HamiltonianCycle class represents a Hamiltonian cycle in a graph.
    IEdge
    The IEdge interface represents an edge in a graph.
    IGraph
    The IGraph interface represents a graph.
    Node
    The Node class represents a node in a graph.
    WeightedGraph
    The WeightedGraph class represents a weighted graph.
